<!-- OVERVIEW SECTION -->
<h2>📖 Project Overview</h2>
<p>
  <b>LabProject</b> is a comprehensive Clinical Operations Platform designed to manage the entire lifecycle of diagnostic testing. From the moment a specimen is accessioned to the automated delivery of AI-interpreted results, the system ensures data integrity, clinical compliance, and financial transparency. 
</p>
<p>
  The platform serves five distinct user personas, providing each with mission-critical tools: <b>Lab Administrators</b> (Ops Monitoring), <b>Clinicians</b> (Result Verification), <b>Referring Doctors</b> (Patient Tracking), <b>Patients</b> (Portal Access), and <b>Finance Teams</b> (Revenue Management).
</p>

