<!-- CONTRIBUTIONS SECTION -->
<h2>🛠️ Engineering Contributions & Governance</h2>

<table>
  <tr>
    <td width="50%">
      <h3>📊 Visualization Governance</h3>
      <p>Standardized analytics across <b>Chart.js</b> and <b>Flot</b>. Introduced module-aware palettes (Operations, Accounting, Appointments) to prevent context-switching fatigue for users managing high-density data.</p>
    </td>
    <td width="50%">
      <h3>🤖 AI Operationalization</h3>
      <p>Architected a compliance-first AI layer. Managed provider failover (OpenAI/Anthropic), implemented branch-level cost caps, and enforced mandatory non-diagnostic disclaimers for patient safety.</p>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="50%">
      <h3>📅 Resource Management</h3>
      <p>Engineered a conflict-aware scheduling engine. Unlike standard booking, this logic accounts for medical setup/cleanup buffers and branch-specific resource constraints.</p>
    </td>
    <td width="50%">
      <h3>💰 Financial Integrity</h3>
      <p>Built a secure doctor commission wallet. Features include configurable referral rules, automated webhook-triggered credits, and a transparent payout reconciliation workflow.</p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

